sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant W as WebUI
  participant G as Gateway
  participant GG as Google
  U->>W: login
  W->>GG: redirect (auth code)
  GG-->>U: consent
  U->>GG: approve
  GG-->>W: code
  W->>G: code
  G->>GG: token exchange
  GG-->>G: id_token
  G->>G: verify (JWKS, aud, iss)
  G-->>W: session cookie
